Name: Highland Empty Plot
Highlights: Strategically located empty plot in the fast-growing suburban area of Albany, offering an excellent opportunity for commercial or residential development.
Zoned for both commercial and residential use, providing flexibility for potential buyers to develop office spaces, retail centers, or residential apartments.
Proximity to key infrastructure, including schools, hospitals, shopping malls, and parks, making it an attractive location for families and businesses.
Available utilities include water, electricity, and sewage systems, reducing the initial setup costs for future construction projects.

ValueParameters.description: Albany's suburban areas are expanding rapidly, with an increasing demand for residential and commercial spaces due to the city's growth.
The local government's flexible zoning regulations make it easier to develop a variety of structures on the plot, attracting more investors.

Proposals.name: Capital Developers
Proposals.description: Capital Developers proposes to construct a mixed-use complex on the plot, featuring retail and residential units.

Proposals.name: Urban Commercial Ltd.
Proposals.description: Urban Commercial Ltd. plans to develop a modern office complex to attract businesses looking for premium office spaces in the Albany area.
